{"tid":1704193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5個月 希望大家醒覺","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:58:37.000Z","uid":115323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80fe707d6513d991cfb61b1bd516cc5a318745d0","tid":1704193,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"次次發夢叫口號 屌鳩克警 但次次結果都係好撚多人比狗拉 比狗打  <br />\n到有人死就全世界一齊RIP <br />\n然後查案既查案 比你查到 咁又點?乜到呢一刻仲覺得有法治?<br />\n法律真係可以制裁克警?<br />\n唔好問我有咩高見 我諗呢個答案其實好多人都心裡有數 <br />\n只係想提醒大家再唔改變好快就輸 <br />\n我地仲有幾多個月玩?仲有幾多義士要比人拉?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11.11三罷  有你有我</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5d1445067ed9d1a4c93bf671657193121526d519","tid":1704193,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"醒覺唔好再搵支那<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=8890452f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws9KMEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws9KMEO.jpg&h=ae373530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong Independence Party <br />\n5 agendas </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(1)  UK has the mandate from the People of Hong Kong to annul the Sino-British Joint Declaration right away; Also should the US subsequently abolish the HK Policy Act.<br />\n<br />\n(2) the UK and the US governments are requested by the Hongkongers for taking on the PRC&rsquo;s illegal occupation of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n(3)  We require the United Kingdom to enforce those three unterminated treaties over Hong Kong sovereignty ( the Treaty of Nanking; the Convention of Peking; the Second Convention of Peking ).<br />\n<br />\n(4) We demand Anglo-American or Nato joint military base in Hong Kong on a permanent basis, the expense of which will be covered by ourselves!<br />\n<br />\n(5) Hong Kong should and is going to be an independent Commonwealth nation.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=8890452f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a>"},{"pid":"e368869b0f66476ae0e49672d52fae2bc3633949","tid":1704193,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e81163daa673f07829800b3d843329c90d8788a","tid":1704193,"uid":238984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"CHINA<br />\n- Complete withdrawal of extradition bill<br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry<br />\n- No riot labeling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nC.H.I.N.A.<br />\nFive demands Not one less"},{"pid":"8d353fe3b8deeeaeb6dddb6eab355b23ffb0db4d","tid":1704193,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正攬炒</span></span><br />\n阻鳩交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出黎<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-<br />\n雙十一，周圍塞，阻塞交通變相全民罷工 悼念完一定要有行動，手足既血不可白流<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 扮工師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【召集和理非】聽朝7點唔知點做好？入嚟睇下有咩最簡單嘅嘢可以做！<br />\n<a href=\"ht